### Features

✅ Save picture

✅ Choose number of picture

✅ Very cute waifu ❤ (Very Important)

### Installation

You need to install any dependencies needed for the downloader
```
dart pub add http
```

To start the downloader u just need to type that
```
dart .\main.dart
```
